response.original_title: Club Nights - DJ Mark Sanchez Live at the Amphitheater
response.overview: DJ Mark Sanchez live DVD filmed at Santoro's Amphitheater in Ybor City Florida.  Groove for 78 Minutes of pulse pounding Breakbeats and Hard House tracks with 100% live video footage of the show.  Featuring footage from the dance floor, VIP, and backstage.  Florida's hottest girls and guys come out to party with one of Florida's hottest DJs in a kick-ass venue!  Includes bonus footage with Jackal & Hyde, DJ Ashley, Playgurl, & DJ Trixie
